Author: punsandprose
Text: Better doesn't mean fatter. You could look less pale, your eyes are brighter and not tired looking or dark circles, you seem more alert, you smile more, your skin looks glowier, your hair looks thicker, your lips aren't dry, etc  there are plenty of visual side effects to eds that improve as you up your intake, it doesn't mean you look "fatter"  But my mind usually goes there too ):
